{"tid":775716,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪每個人都會跌入傷感嘅漩渦？","createTime":"2018-08-11T11:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T06:16:05.000Z","uid":194168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b5cd81634f319ec00a9efdeb25af73f84e6a7da8","tid":775716,"uid":194168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:30:52.000Z","msg":"標題可能寫到1999，話說我發現自己好易一唔開心就亂諗嘢，但明明平時都無乜嘢好樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假設我同人鬧交，就會瘋狂諗佢以前點樣對我好，小小事都諗起佢（明明之前無事嗰陣都無咁掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，又或者會諗一啲佢曾經做過嘅嘢，去印證自己「佢對我好差」嘅諗法，但明明無事嗰陣覺得呢啲小事wfc。最後就會推論到一大堆所謂嘅「做人道理」，例如唔好太愛一個人呀、對一件事唔好太上心呀、所有人都係人性本惡呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">如果真係傷心完就傷心完都由至可，最撚戇鳩嘅係傷心完，回復正常，呢啲放大咗嘅諗法都可能會喺個腦度出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n究竟係正常人都會咁、某一類人會咁，定得我係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf404911706960d8ed2390ef2f88687009092a0","tid":775716,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"人之常情"},{"pid":"e8436fdac52a58dd1eabcc406ab7754a0772f653","tid":775716,"uid":194168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf404911706960d8ed2390ef2f88687009092a0","tid":775716,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"人之常情"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"傷心嗰陣個個都會瘋狂亂諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4499eeccd58610979d10da1b5ec214161cda897b","tid":775716,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8436fdac52a58dd1eabcc406ab7754a0772f653","tid":775716,"uid":194168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf404911706960d8ed2390ef2f88687009092a0","tid":775716,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:39:03.0